&lt;p&gt;The quiet rhythm of sanding is one of the most honest sounds in making. Picture a Saturday afternoon: sunlight across the bench, a project that matters—maybe the oak table your family eats at, a guitar body you’ve been shaping for months, or a door panel you’re finally prepping for paint. You feel the surface more than you see it. The paper whispers over high spots, snags a little on a nick you missed. Instinct nudges the next move—do you keep the tactile connection of hand sanding, or pick up the block to force the surface true?&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/05.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2026/01/10/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/block-or-bare-hand-when-to-use-each-method-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>12</readingTime></item><item><title>How To Keep Pressure Even During Hand Sanding</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 21 Dec 2025 13:33:29 +0000</pubDate><category>Hand Sanding Techniques</category><category>grit-80</category><category>grit-220</category><category>sanding block</category><category>grit progression</category><description>Learn how to keep pressure even during hand sanding with pro body mechanics, blocks, grit strategy, and checks for perfect flats and curves.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="even-pressure-mastery-in-hand-sanding"&gt;Even Pressure Mastery in Hand Sanding&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A fresh sheet of paper crackles between your fingers as you kneel beside a project you’ve put your evenings into—a walnut coffee table top you milled by hand, or maybe a maple guitar body you’ve been carving between jobs. You tell yourself it’s “just sanding,” but you know better. One wrong move and a finger groove shows up under the finish. One heavy corner and the veneer starts to whisper thin. The difference between amateur and pro often shows up right here, during hand sanding, in the quiet, repetitive passes that bring wood to life.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/18.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/21/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/how-to-keep-pressure-even-during-hand-sanding-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>13</readingTime></item><item><title>Wrap Sandpaper Around Dowels For Curved Edges</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 05 Dec 2025 13:37:54 +0000</pubDate><category>Hand Sanding Techniques</category><category>grit-120</category><category>grit-150</category><category>grit-180</category><category>grit-220</category><category>grit-240</category><category>grit-320</category><category>grit-400</category><category>grit-600</category><category>grit-800</category><category>grit progression</category><description>Practical guide to hand sanding curved edges by wrapping sandpaper around dowels; testing abrasives, grits, and jigs for consistent radii.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="hand-sanding-curves-wrap-paper-around-dowels"&gt;Hand Sanding Curves: Wrap Paper Around Dowels&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I remember the first time a curve made me question my craft. It was a walnut keepsake box with a lid that looked perfect on CAD: a soft 10 mm radius running cleanly along all four edges. On the bench, though, the radius fought back. My block sander flattened the apex, my random-orbit sander skated off the edge, and every “shortcut” I tried left flats and chatter marks that showed up under finish like neon. I finally reached for the simplest tool in the shop: a hardwood dowel, a strip of abrasive, and my hands. With careful hand sanding—wrapping the paper around a dowel that matched the profile—the radius began to read as a continuous curve instead of a sequence of mistakes. The tactile feedback told me where the high spots were; the scratch pattern told me when I was pushing too hard.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/02.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/12/05/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/wrap-sandpaper-around-dowels-for-curved-edges-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>12</readingTime></item><item><title>Hand Sanding Versus Power Sanding Comparison</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Thu, 20 Nov 2025 16:50:43 +0000</pubDate><category>Hand Sanding Techniques</category><category>grit-120</category><category>grit-180</category><category>grit-320</category><category>grit progression</category><description>Engineer’s comparison of hand sanding and power sanding: surface finish, speed, dust, cost, and workflow tips for wood, metal, and paint.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="hand-sanding-vs-power-sanding-an-engineers-guide"&gt;Hand sanding vs power sanding: an engineer’s guide&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;There’s a point in every restoration or build where the project stops looking like a collection of parts and starts feeling like an object with a future. For me, it’s the first moment the surface turns uniformly matte under the light. That’s usually after the first disciplined pass of hand sanding. The radio is low, dust extraction hums in the background, and the world reduces to the consistent rhythm of the block. Compare that to the blunt urgency of a random-orbit sander—faster, louder, and undeniably effective. Both have their place. When you’re staring at a hardwood tabletop with coffee rings and cross-grain scratches, or a steel bracket that needs a satin finish without rounding its crisp edges, the choice between manual strokes and powered oscillations is more than preference; it’s a process decision that dictates speed, quality, and cost.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/images/brand/17.webp" medium="image"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/pinterest/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/20/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/hand-sanding-versus-power-sanding-comparison-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><readingTime>11</readingTime></item><item><title>Choose Sanding Direction To Follow The Grain</title><link>https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/09/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/09/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding/</guid><pubDate>Sun, 09 Nov 2025 18:57:00 +0000</pubDate><category>Hand Sanding Techniques</category><category>grit-60</category><category>grit-80</category><category>grit-100</category><category>grit-120</category><category>grit-150</category><category>grit-180</category><category>grit-220</category><category>grit-320</category><category>grit-400</category><category>grit-500</category><description>Learn how to choose sanding direction, optimize abrasive performance, and master hand sanding workflows for flawless, grain-aligned wood surfaces.</description><summary>&lt;h2 id="hand-sanding-with-the-grain-direction-that-wins"&gt;Hand Sanding With the Grain: Direction That Wins&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The first pass across the old walnut dresser felt almost sacrilegious. Early light from the shop window caught the cathedral patterns in the veneer and made the scratches I’d inherited glow silver against the warm brown. Years of hasty refinishes had left low, cross-grain swirls that refused to disappear under fresh film. I set the random-orbit sander aside, reached for a cork block, and let the board tell me where it wanted me to go. In that moment, hand sanding was not about nostalgia—it was about control. Fingers learned the flow of the fibers, eyes trained on the raking light, strokes tracking the grain like a compass needle finally finding north.&lt;/p&gt;</summary><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/09/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/09/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/09/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding/cards/facebook/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/09/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding.jpg" medium="image"/><media:thumbnail url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/09/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding.jpg"/><enclosure url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/2025/11/09/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding/cards/instagram/choose-sanding-direction-to-follow-the-grain-hand-sanding.jpg" type="image/jpeg"/><media:content url="https://blog.equalle.com/posts/20